  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The leadership of the community, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in a very broad sense and certainly in a historic sense, has failed [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jewish leadership [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] has failed or-- perhaps in large measure as a result of circumstances or not because of their own fault.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They were paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they, by and large, insisted on hanging on to these most unrealistic and impractical notion that the community and the city was going to be unharmed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one of the sinful results of it was that it was difficult to get [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] help for those who were already, in effect, in the ghetto-- although they were then moved into another location in, in, in what became the ghetto-- until virtually the last day.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have to this day-- I have all sorts of difficulties with this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember a former president of the community that I went to and asked him to give me money so I could buy food and, and clothing or whatever for the people who had been brought in before we were put into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he virtually threw me out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In a way, it's, it's quite understandable, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- aside from the fact that they, they could not cope with-- they couldn't expect it to be-- to cope with the events.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was, it was not conceivable for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so you simply couldn't be prepared for it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And aside from the fact that there was a total dislocation and disorientation.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
